			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Watch out for these guys. It is -possible- for a level 16 caster to solo these things, but the only caster I've seen do it is my necro, and I died every third attempt - so it wasn't worth it.<BR>
<BR>
At level 20, these things become much more possible solo prety, especially for the kiters. They hit for 42 damage, so your level 16 pet is going to be done in about 8 hits, and if you're a caster, even buffed you won't stand up long to these.<BR>
<BR>
Best solution for these is to:<BR>
a) use tank and big nukes or major dots.<BR>
b) use pet, dots, and fear kite w/darkness or ensnare.<BR>
<BR>
p.s. the eyes do drop individually sometimes, in regards to the person who said the eyes drop in pairs.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
