				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Okay here is what I have to say,<BR>
Garg's are lvl 18-19... they con green at lvl 27,<BR>
Also about 75% are lvl 19 and 25% are 18<BR>
The gargolye eye drops about 25% of the time, and sells for over 9pp if you have relativly high charisma. Also this Is a bad place to start trains, cause you can't swim to safety, the garg can swim just as fast as he can run! If you want to fight here be AT LEAST lvl 18, and if you group, try to have an enchanter with you, the enchanter can stop trains in case you cause them and a train on this isle means death, I had to save my group many a time!, just make sure you enchanter has Color Flux, Enthrall, Memory Blur, and mabye even Mezmerize for extra safety. <BR>
Happy hunting!<BR>
